<item>
            <title>[LU-17047] interop rolling-downgrade-client2 sanity test_77c: no checksum dump file on OSS</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17047</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;adilger@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/8781ed4d-a81d-48bb-bde9-46557c0a8bd2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/8781ed4d-a81d-48bb-bde9-46557c0a8bd2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_77c failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;onyx-124vm11 ls -checksum_dump-ost-\[0x20002abb4:0x98a5:0x0]*
onyx-124vm11: ls: cannot access &apos;&apos;$&apos;\003&apos;&apos;-checksum_dump-ost-[0x20002abb4:0x98a5:0x0]*&apos;: No such file or directory
 sanity test_77c: @@@@@@ FAIL: no checksum dump file on OSS 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_12/164&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_12/164&lt;/a&gt; - 3.10.0-1160.49.1.el7.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4440&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4440&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-477.10.1.el8_lustre.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This started failing on 2023-06-22 and appears to be related to the rolling-downgrade-client2 session.&lt;/p&gt;







&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
sanity test_77c - no checksum dump file on OSS&lt;/p&gt;</description>
